headline.main: LOUIS D. BRANDEIS, RETIRED JUSTICE, DIES AT CAPITAL; Member of the Supreme Court for 23 Years Succumbs to Heart Attack at 84

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Oct. 5 -- Louis Dembitz Brandeis, retired Associate Justice of the Supreme Court and one of the greatest liberals in the history of that tribunal, died at his residence here at 7:15 o'clock this evening.
